OL,3,CWest Midlands fire boss suspended
OL,5,FThe boss of West Midlands Fire Service
OL,6,F(WMFS) has been suspended from his
OL,7,Fpost.
OL,9,FMr Lee was appointed chief executive
OL,10,Fon an interim basis in March following
OL,11,Fthe death of chief Wayne Brown in
OL,12,FJanuary.
OL,14,FThe fire service released a statement
OL,15,Fon 7 October saying the decision to
OL,16,Fsuspend Mr Lee is "not one it ever
OL,17,Fwanted to have take or takes lightly".
