OL,3,CWest Midlands fire boss suspended
OL,5,FIt said the authority took independent
OL,6,Flegal advice before making the
OL,7,Fdecision, which is subject to
OL,8,Fratification on 14 October.
OL,10,F"If this is upheld, a process to
OL,11,Fappoint an independent person to
OL,12,Finvestigate will be undertaken. You
OL,13,Fwill understand that it would not be
OL,14,Fright to comment further on the
OL,15,Fspecifics", the statement read.
