OL,3,CWest Midlands fire boss suspended
OL,5,F"In what has been a very difficult
OL,6,Fyear for West Midlands Fire Service
OL,7,F(WMFS), it is hugely deflating for all
OL,8,Finvolved that we have reached this
OL,9,Fpoint, and we realise this will cause
OL,10,Ffurther public concern."
OL,12,FBut, the statement read, the service
OL,13,Fremains "fully focused" on delivering
OL,14,Fa "vital and outstanding" emergency
OL,15,Fservice.
OL,17,FLast month, the interim boss Mr Lee
OL,18,Fsaid he had turned down the permanent
OL,19,Fposition of fire cheif and described
OL,20,Fthe authority's governance as being
OL,21,F"wholly impossible".
