OL,3,CWest Midlands fire boss suspended
OL,5,FDirectly addressing the incident, the
OL,6,Fstatement said: "The issues that Mr
OL,7,FLee raised publicly concerning the
OL,8,Fgovernance of the Fire and Rescue
OL,9,FService will continue to be
OL,10,Finvestigated independently, and
OL,11,Freported to the Fire Authority for
OL,12,Fconsideration.
OL,14,F"They will also share such findings
OL,15,Fwith our external auditors, His
OL,16,FMajesty's Inspectorate of Constabulary
OL,17,Fand Fire and Rescue Services, and
OL,18,Fother such key stakeholders as
OL,19,Fnecessary."
